description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a CPD Coordinator to work as part of an NHS Learning and Development Team. The post holder will provide administrative services on behalf of Learning and Development for the full range of specialist skills post- registration development courses (SSPRD) and education programmes delivered via universities, further education institutes and external training providers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will have responsibility for administering the Trusts external study leave process as well as the funding streams associated with external training, education, learning and development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience of working within a Learning and Development environment and experience of administering study leave processes is essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information please contact Kerry Gillott, Learning and Leadership Development Manager at kerry.gillott@swyt.nhs.uk or phone 07785 414004.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
